GIST Framework Academic Research Notice

This software implements the GIST (Governance, Infrastructure, Security, Trust)
Framework developed as part of academic research on digital maturity assessment
in the Italian retail sector (Grande Distribuzione Organizzata - GDO).

The framework is based on empirical research involving 234 organizations and
has been validated through statistical analysis and expert review processes.

When using this software in academic or commercial contexts, please consider
citing the original research work.

